    q: "Can you migrate our existing store to Shopify without losing SEO rankings?",
    a: "Yes. Store migration requires careful 301 redirect mapping from old URLs to new ones to preserve your Google rankings. We create a complete URL mapping document before migration and implement all redirects on launch day. We also re-submit your sitemap to Google after migration and monitor rankings in the weeks following launch."
  },
  {
    q: "What is the typical conversion rate for Indian e-commerce stores?",
    a: "The average Indian e-commerce store converts at 1.5 to 2 percent. Well-optimised stores with fast loading, clear product information, and smooth checkout typically achieve 3 to 4 percent. The clients we have worked with on conversion rate optimisation have seen their rates improve from 1.2 percent to 3.4 percent on average after our audit and optimisation process."
  },
