  },
  {
    q: "How does Google Shopping work and is it worth the investment for Indian stores?",
    a: "Google Shopping shows your product image, name, price, and rating directly in Google search results when someone searches for a product you sell. It typically delivers a higher click-through rate than standard text ads because buyers can see the product and price before clicking. For product-based businesses in India, Shopping campaigns almost always deliver better return on ad spend than standard search ads alone."
  },
  {
    q: "Can you set up COD (cash on delivery) on our store?",
    a: "Yes. Cash on delivery is still widely used in India, particularly in tier 2 and tier 3 cities. We configure COD as a payment option in your store and can set up COD limits by order value or pin code if needed. We also help you set up Shiprocket or other shipping integrations that handle COD collection and remittance."
